sending `x` to `(f x)‚Åª¬π`. -/
@[to_additive]
instance : has_inv (A ‚Üí*[n] G) :=
‚ü®Œª f, { to_fun := Œª x, (f x)‚Åª¬π,
  map_prod_eq_map_prod' := Œª s t hsA htA hs ht h,
